Comment: 10,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ủa?
Comment: 10,0:14:06.43,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a witch?
Comment: 10,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got the fourth ingredient.
Comment: 10,0:14:18.88,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Last is a traditional medicine base made by a yeti.
Comment: 10,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to see the yeti?
Comment: 10,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Comment: 10,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he lives at the base of that mountain.
Comment: 10,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So far!
Comment: 10,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ride this to get there.
Comment: 10,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 10,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Wait for me, guys.{## yeah i know she's including the parents too, but eh}
