Comment: 10,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you promise me?
Comment: 10,0:16:55.58,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I explain to you that I'm in big trouble if you can't make the medicine base for the antidote?!
