Comment: 10,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Hey, wait!
Comment: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Sao thế?
Comment: 10,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop!
